question: What would someone not know about you when they first meet you?
If you could change anything about the way you were raised, what would it be?
If you could change one thing about yourself, what would it be? Would you actually change it?
What is a defining moment in your life that changed the way you viewed the world?
Show us a photo that means a lot to you and tell us the story behind it
What types of books would we find on your bookshelf? Which book (or podcast) has most influenced you?
What is something you have always wanted to learn, but havent yet?
What is something you are currently being challenged by?
Describe a ten out of ten day for you. Have you had one? If so, what happened?
What are you thankful for at this very moment?
What does a good life mean to you?
If at the end of the year, you had accomplished one thing, what would make the biggest difference to your happiness?
What is the most meaningful trip you have been on? What made this trip unique?
What could you talk about for hours?
What is a place that has a lot of meaning to you and why?
Who is the most influential person in your life?
If we knew you well, what would we know you were grateful for? What if we knew you really well?
When you think about your life, what do you find most astonishing and why?
What movie or TV show would you recommend to someone to get a feel for your personality?
What is something beautiful you've seen or felt recently?
When was the last time you cried?
What moment in your family history would you have wanted to see?
If you had one question to get to know someone, what would it be? What would be your answer?
If you could go back and rewatch one scene in your life without changing it, what would it be?
What is the best meal you have ever had?
What is your most memorable childhood memory? How has it impacted you?
What is your most treasured or most terrible memory?
If you could hold on to one memory from your life forever, what would that be?
What matters to you that may not matter for others?
What is one thing from this year, big or small, that you are proud of?
What is a song that is attached to a strong memory or feeling for you? What is the feeling and what is its origin story?
What has been on your mind recently?
What is something you wish people understood about you? And why?
